data.description: Amazing 4 bedroom home in Goodnight Ranch is up for grabs. This beauty has a large family room with a brick fireplace as the focal point. The kitchen boast recessed lighting, breakfast area, pantry and plenty of cabinets and counter space to store all your gadgets. The master suite is bright and airy accompanied by a private bath and walk in closet. Bedrooms 2, 3 & 4 all have carpet flooring, ample closet space and sizable windows drawing in natural light. Get ready to host football parties in the over-sized backyard closed in by a privacy fence. Come take your tour day!
